name: OCKCompletionRingButton.CompletionState
desc: A set of cases that specify the completion state.

items.name: case dimmed
items.desc: A case that indicates the ring button is disabled.

items.name: case empty
items.desc: A case that indicates the completion state is empty.

items.name: case progress(CGFloat)
items.desc: A case that indicates the completion progress for the ring; completion ranges from 0, which indicates no progress, to 1.0, which indicates 100% progress.

items.name: case zero
items.desc: A case that indicates the completion state is zero.
